            typedef struct  { float WetDryMix; float Feedback; float Delay;	
            } ;	

             Members	

WetDryMix Ratio of wet (processed) signal to dry (original) signal. 	

Feedback Amount of output to feed back into input. 	

Delay Delay to all channels in milliseconds. This value must be between FXECHO_MIN_DELAY and FXECHO_INITDATA.MaxDelay.



