            typedef struct  { float Diffusion; float RoomSize;	
            } ;	

             Members	

Diffusion Controls the character of the individual wall reflections. Set to minimum value to simulate a hard flat surface and to maximum value to simulate a diffuse surface.Value must be between FXREVERB_MIN_DIFFUSION and FXREVERB_MAX_DIFFUSION. 	

RoomSize Size of the room. Value must be between FXREVERB_MIN_ROOMSIZE and FXREVERB_MAX_ROOMSIZE. Note that physical meaning of RoomSize is subjective and not tied to any particular units. A smaller value will result in reflections reaching the listener more quickly while reflections will take longer with larger values for RoomSize.
